					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak with Dead dialog with Nettie, Halsin's apprentice. Nettie likely died while trying to kill the player by poisoning them. She didn't want to, but did it to protect the grove, knowing that you might transform into a monster that would kill everyone there."
